game.name: Cake Eaters
game.description:
Cake lovers are everywhere. Today luckily you have got many cakes but with a great number of thieves who want to steal them at any cost. You as the protector of those cakes do not want to lose them. The only way to save them from the thieves is to put your shooting abilities to test. Do you think that you are ready now to accept this challenge? Jon Cake Eaters and be prepared to shoot all these thieves before they attack on your fav dish!
Remember these cake eaters are very fast and keep coming from the top of the screen. All you need to do is put your fingers on the mouse if you try it out on your PC or touch the screen if you play this online cooking game on your mobile phone. Play wisely to get the maximum possible scores and show the world that you have expertise in shooting! You are sure to have a great fun while defending all your cakes in this one of the best games for girls.
Faces of these cake eaters resemble with each other. So, keep shooting the same faces more times to make them disappear on the screen. Shoot with LMC and aim your target through mouse. It is a wonderful opportunity to save more and more cakes for you and enjoy them at every night. Our website features a countless selection of free cake games for kids. All it takes a gaming device with a proper internet connectivity to play girls games online as many times as you want.
